name: Disney's Donald Duck: Goin' Quackers
overview: Donald is goin' quackers! Donald runs amuck, goes berserk, and gets hyper across 20 levels in 4 cartoon-like worlds in this hilarious quest to rescue Daisy. - Features favorite characters: Daisy, Huey, Dewey, Louie, the Beagle Boys and more. - Control Donald's explosive temper, confront wacky characters and obstacles. - It's non-stop action as Donald runs, jumps, dodges and quacks his way to save Daisy!
